des:
Use Alexa to voice control your HomeBud products!

To get started, please connect Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our "HomeBud" app in app store, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in "HomeBud" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable "HomeBud" skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say "Search complete";
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the light.
Alexa, open the blind.
Alexa, close the blind.
Alexa, open the blind to 20%.
Alexa, turn off the plug.
